<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:10:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军警告真主党如果加沙谈判破裂，准备与以色列长期战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-warns-hezbollah-bracing-for-prolonged-fighting-with-israel-if-gaza-talks-collapse/00000191-d668-d457-a3f9-dfff8e830000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡内阁的一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“即使是现在，战争已经过去近一年了，内塔尼亚胡所宣称的目标都没有实现”；尽管总理最近声称，让北方居民返回家园并不是正式的战争目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 16:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-warns-hezbollah-bracing-for-prolonged-fighting-with-israel-if-gaza-talks-collapse/00000191-d668-d457-a3f9-dfff8e830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女在特拉维夫海滩向部长本格维尔投掷沙子 警方起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/police-indicts-israeli-woman-for-throwing-sand-at-minister-ben-gvir-at-tel-aviv-beach/00000191-d72b-db7f-abd3-f7afd4080000</link><description>27 岁的诺亚·戈登伯格 (Noa Goldenberg) 因袭击公务员和妨碍警察而被起诉，每项指控将面临最高三年的监禁。她因涉嫌向国家安全部长扔湿泥而被捕</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/police-indicts-israeli-woman-for-throwing-sand-at-minister-ben-gvir-at-tel-aviv-beach/00000191-d72b-db7f-abd3-f7afd4080000</guid></item><item><title>吞并、驱逐和以色列定居点：内塔尼亚胡为加沙战争的下一阶段做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/annexation-expulsion-and-settlements-netanyahu-gears-up-for-next-phase-of-gaza-war/00000191-d739-dba7-a1ff-dfff26830000</link><description>战争进入新阶段并不是从多师机动或对敌人腹地的大胆袭击开始的。相反，它是通过一份官僚声明而来的，并将让本杰明·内塔尼亚胡梦想着他的支持者将视之为一生的成就</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/annexation-expulsion-and-settlements-netanyahu-gears-up-for-next-phase-of-gaza-war/00000191-d739-dba7-a1ff-dfff26830000</guid></item><item><title>是什么让以色列学生为伊朗情报部门工作？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/what-made-an-israeli-student-work-for-iranian-intelligence/00000191-d656-deec-add7-de57ca1e0000</link><description>伊朗特工正在通过社交媒体接触以色列人，试图招募他们。辛贝特担心越来越多的以色列人愿意与他们合作</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/what-made-an-israeli-student-work-for-iranian-intelligence/00000191-d656-deec-add7-de57ca1e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么特朗普和万斯不会谴责塔克·卡尔森和他否认大屠杀的朋友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-trump-and-vance-wont-condemn-tucker-carlson-and-his-holocaust-denying-pals/00000191-d69a-db58-afbb-defefa580000</link><description>至少唐纳德·特朗普是一贯的。多年来他一直在为反犹太主义者和大屠杀否认者辩护。但作为共和党总统候选人，他与塔克·卡尔森的接近对美国、以色列和全球犹太人构成了明显而现实的危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-trump-and-vance-wont-condemn-tucker-carlson-and-his-holocaust-denying-pals/00000191-d69a-db58-afbb-defefa580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-约旦边境的致命袭击可能使阿卜杜拉国王陷入政治雷区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</link><description>约旦国王巧妙地平衡了内部对以色列的愤怒和维持外交关系的努力。就在约旦人即将投票选出新议会的几天前，袭击者与一个关键支持部落的联系使他的事情变得复杂</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/the-attack-at-the-jordan-border-crossing-poses-a-grave-political-threat-to-king-abdullah/00000191-d5e6-deaf-a1f1-ddf71e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因发布威胁人质母亲的视频而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</link><description>警方逮捕了一名来自以色列北部的男子，据称他发布了一段视频，威胁要袭击已在加沙被关押超过 11 个月的 Matan 的母亲 Einav Zangauker</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:24:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arrested-for-publishing-threatening-video-against-hostages-mother/00000191-d63c-dec1-add7-f7ff4c890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队告诉家人，在被谋杀的加沙人质上发现了防御伤痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</link><description>以色列国防军上周取回了人质的尸体，并表示他们在士兵抵达前不久被处决。据一名人质亲属称，家人被告知隧道内场面混乱，人质身上发现有防御伤痕</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/defense-wounds-found-on-murdered-gaza-hostages-israeli-army-tells-families/00000191-d5a6-df60-a79b-d5fffe670000</guid></item><item><title>枪、辫子和警惕的眼睛：这位埃塞俄比亚以色列艺术家拒绝陈词滥调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</link><description>雷切尔·安约 (Rachel Anyo) 掌控了自己的叙事，创作出具有挑衅性的作品，直面黑人女性气质、潜在的暴力和社会期望，并大胆拒绝强加给她的谦虚</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/guns-braids-and-watchful-eyes-this-ethiopian-israeli-artist-refuses-to-be-a-cliche/00000191-d239-d214-a393-d7b917740000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡请求法院阻止在即将上映的电影中播放他的审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</link><description>耶路撒冷法院在提交请愿书后不久就驳回了请愿书，距离“比比档案”计划在多伦多电影节首映几个小时</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-court-to-block-airing-of-his-interrogation-in-upcoming-film/00000191-d5e9-deaf-a1f1-ddff45940000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列袭击了叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的地点，包括化学武器设施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</link><description>叙利亚官方媒体称以色列连夜对哈马附近发动袭击 反对派战争监察员称七人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:47:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/report-israel-strikes-iranian-sites-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d537-d25e-a1f7-d7bf512e0000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都会为司法部长对司法系统的痴迷付出代价，甚至可能是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</link><description>以色列最高法院的法官们别无选择，被迫拒绝命令司法部长遵守法律条文，召开一年多没有开会的司法任命委员会，以便它可以根据资历制度选举新的最高法院院长</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 04:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article/.premium/all-israelis-will-pay-for-levins-obsession-with-the-judiciary-maybe-even-netanyahu/00000191-d347-d25e-a1f7-d7cf2b6f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医务人员报告周一有 20 名巴勒斯坦人死亡；黎巴嫩火箭袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</link><description>黎巴嫩纳哈里亚住宅楼遭大火袭击 ■ 叙利亚称，以色列发动的袭击造成 18 人死亡，其中包括武器开发中心 ■ 以色列国防军呼吁加沙西北部居民在火箭弹袭击后撤离家园 ■ 强调，约旦谴责艾伦比渡口恐怖袭击需要两国解决方案</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-09/ty-article-live/reports-israel-struck-several-targets-in-syria-including-scientific-research-facility/00000191-d4b2-d83f-a3d9-ddfbf7310005</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长预计推迟任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</link><description>一位与司法部长亚里夫·莱文关系密切的人士表示，“他不会做一个好孩子，安静地接受裁决”，他指的是最高法院要求他必须任命一位新总统的裁决，“但他也不会违反这一裁决”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</guid></item><item><title>他们为赫什·戈德堡-波林和奥里·达尼诺而战。在湿婆节，他们见到了家人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</link><description>达尼诺和戈德伯格-波林一家上周在相距几英里的地方举行了湿婆礼，但认识并不是人们来到他们家的先决条件。一位曾拜访过这两家公司的人士表示，“我是来安慰自己的，也希望得到一点安慰”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡自己的话暴露了他的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的说法——哈马斯独自阻止了一项协议——证明了他的策略的失败，如果一开始就有策略的话</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 19:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</guid></item><item><title>“这是我的职责”：是什么让这些活动分子来到约旦河谷的一个巴勒斯坦小镇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列定居者以约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦城镇的al-Auja溪流为目标，切断当地人的水源。一群以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在现场游行，决心因剥夺和战争而“圣化生命”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</guid></item><item><title>摩尔多瓦拒绝批准降落后，乌曼飞往哈西德派犹太人的航班可能会被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</link><description>成千上万想要参观布拉茨拉夫拉比·纳赫曼坟墓的持票人已被告知，摩尔多瓦政府拒绝批准布拉茨拉夫·哈西丁飞经基希讷乌机场。正在探索飞往罗马尼亚的替代航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</guid></item><item><title>目击者称以色列军队在没有发生冲突的情况下射杀了美国活动人士</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</link><description>“我们站着，军队可以看到，只是站在那里什么也不做。什么也没发生。我听到两声枪响，”一位也参加了艾森努尔·埃兹吉·埃吉被杀的示威活动的抗议者说道。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第338天：外国外交官称停战谈判“没有取得任何进展”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</link><description>约旦人向以色列-约旦边境口岸开火，造成三名以色列人死亡 ■ 熟悉停战谈判的消息人士：“只有当双方都认为有兴趣时才会发生” ■ 以色列安全内阁周日晚间讨论协议 ■ 以色列国防军：向北部发射了 50 枚火箭弹以色列从黎巴嫩出发 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人启程参加停火运动，并在埃及和黎巴嫩停留，但不包括以色列 ■ 战争结束 338 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</guid></item></channel></rss>